说小山姆是你的孩子
That Little Sam is your baby.

30
00:07:04,410 --> 00:07:06,290
是的  这非常重要
Yes, now that's very important.

31
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:08,580
让他认为小山姆是他孙子
If he thinks that Little Sam is his grandchild,

32
00:07:08,580 --> 00:07:09,790
