36
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:26,440
我跟他们说  在北境遇见的你
I told them I met you in the North.

37
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:28,330
你讲了是多北的北边吗
Did you tell them how far north?

38
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:31,290
写信的纸没那么大张啦
Well, it wasn't a very large piece of parchment.

39
00:07:31,290 --> 00:07:33,320
你没告诉他们我的真实来历
You didn't tell them where I'm really from?

40
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:35,040
没告诉他们我是野人
You didn't tell them I'm a wildling?

41
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,190
问题是
The thing is...

42
00:07:37,410 --> 00:07:39,380
我父亲不喜欢野人
my father doesn't like wildlings.

43
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:42,190
他希望我能成为男子汉
He hoped I'd make a man of myself by 

44
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:44,120
去"杀几个该死的野人"
"Killing some bloody wildlings,"

45
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:47,730
所以如果可能的话  最好不要提这事
so it's probably a good subject to avoid if at all possible.

46
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,850
我想我们到了
I think we're here.

47
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,570
山姆
Sam.

48
00:08:24,260 --> 00:08:26,250
山姆
Oh, Sam.

49
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:27,690
您好  母亲
Oh, hello, Mother.

50
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:33,090
我还以为再也见不到你了
I never thought I'd see you again.

51
