父亲要我嫁给西蒙·佛索威
Father says I have to marry Symun Fossoway.

55
00:08:45,650 --> 00:08:48,490
-他一口黄牙...  -够了  塔拉
- He has yellow teeth-- - That's enough, Talla.

56
00:08:50,780 --> 00:08:54,880
母亲  这是吉莉
Oh, um, Mother, this is Gilly.

57
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,340
天哪
Oh, my.

58
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:01,440
你真漂亮
You are lovely.

59
