很高兴认识您  塔利夫人
I am happy to know you, Lady Tarly.

60
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:12,030
还有这个
Oh, and this,

61
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:15,170
是我们的儿子山姆威尔
this is our son Samwell.

62
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:21,750
你好啊  小家伙
Hello, little one.

63
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:26,040
我是你的祖母
It's me, your grandmother.

64
00:09:27,980 --> 00:09:29,130
可以抱抱他吗
May I hold him?

65
