当然了
Yes, of course.

66
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:39,980
一看就是个鬼机灵
You have a curious mind, I can tell.

67
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:43,660
跟你爸爸一样  长大了要当学士
You'll be a scholar like your father.

68
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:47,470
父亲去哪儿了  狄肯呢
Where is Father? And Dickon?

69
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,590
