He killed a white walker.

198
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,480
那根本不存在
There's no such thing.

199
00:18:08,130 --> 00:18:11,560
我们南下去黑城堡的路上我亲眼所见
I saw it with my own eyes on our way down to Castle Black.

200
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:14,790
