他是你俩永远比不上的伟大勇士
He's a greater warrior than either of you will ever be.

203
00:18:24,860 --> 00:18:27,300
你们南下去黑城堡的路上
Your way down to Castle Black?

204
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:32,680
你在哪儿杀的异鬼
Where did he kill a white walker?

205
00:18:35,370 --> 00:18:36,930
