Where are you from?

206
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:39,150
你怎么遇见我儿子的
How'd you come to meet my son?

207
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:44,570
守夜人来了我们的堡垒
The Night's Watch came to our keep.

208
00:18:44,630 --> 00:18:46,300
-在哪里  -吉莉
- Where? - Gilly.

209
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:48,560
-长城以北  -长城以北
- North of the Wall. - North of the Wall?

210
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,890
你是野人
You're a wildling.

211
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:04,420
七国对这些野蛮人
The Seven Kingdoms have waged war

212
00:19:04,420 --> 00:19:06,480
