against these savages for centuries

213
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:09,890
我却在自家大厅里招待了一个
and here I sit hosting one in my hall

214
00:19:11,850 --> 00:19:13,290
多亏了我儿子
thanks to my son.

215
00:19:15,980 --> 00:19:17,350
看见那柄剑了吗
See that sword?

216
00:19:19,840 --> 00:19:21,540
它叫碎心
It's called Heartsbane.

217
00:19:23,360 --> 00:19:26,140
在我们家族传承了五百年
It's been in our family for 500 years.

218
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,540
它是一把瓦雷利亚钢剑
It's Valyrian steel.

219
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:31,590
世上屈指可数
Only a handful of them left in the world.

220
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:35,050
本该在我死后  传给我的长子
It's supposed to go to my firstborn son after I die.

221
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,180
传给他
To him.

222
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:41,730
他永远用不了那剑
He will never wield that sword.

223
00:19:42,690 --> 00:19:45,880
他要是成为角陵伯爵
If he were to become Lord Tarly of Horn Hill,

224
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:48,080
