He dishonors us.

239
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:42,940
你让你自己蒙羞
You dishonor yourself.

240
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:51,360
你母亲是个好人  你配不上她
Your mother's a fine woman. You're not worthy of her.

241
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:56,040
为了哄她开心  我会接纳野人
To please her, I'll take the wildling in.

242
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,640
她可以在厨房干活
She can work in the kitchens.

243
00:20:58,370 --> 00:21:01,320
你的野种交给家里抚养
The bastard will be raised here.

244
00:21:04,390 --> 00:21:07,700
但这是你在角陵待的最后一夜
But this will be the last night you ever spend at Horn Hill.

245
00:21:15,710 --> 00:21:17,550
抱歉  我放任他那样对待你
I'm sorry I let him treat you that way.

246
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:21,570
我担心他不肯接纳你和小山姆
I was afraid he'd turn you and Little Sam away.

247
00:21:22,870 --> 00:21:24,560
我不生你的气
I'm not angry at you.

248
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:27,440
我生气的是
I'm angry that horrible people

249
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:30,090
坏人那样对待好人  却不遭报应
can treat good people that way and get away with it.

250
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:37,180
你什么时候出发
When do you have to go?

251
