天亮就走
First light.

252
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:54,870
代我跟他道别
Say good-bye to him for me.

253
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:05,530
你不是他说的那种人  山姆
You're not what he thinks you are, Sam.

254
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:08,250
他不知道你是什么样的人
He doesn't know what you are.

255
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:13,550
再见  吉莉
Good-bye, Gilly.

256
00:22:58,930 --> 00:23:00,290
-山姆  -我们走
- Sam? - We're leaving.

257
00:23:00,570 --> 00:23:02,620
-什么  -收拾行李
- What? - Get your things.

258
00:23:03,170 --> 00:23:05,040
我没有行李
I don't have any things.

259
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:07,890
-你在做什么  -我们应该在一起
- What are you doing? - We belong together.

260
00:23:08,460 --> 00:23:09,630
我们仨
All of us.

261
00:23:11,470 --> 00:23:12,940
你母亲和妹妹怎么办
What about your mother and sister?

262
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:14,480
她们会理解的
Oh, they'll understand.

263
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:16,680
你妹妹的裙子
Your sister's dress.

264
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:18,160
她不会在意的
She won't mind.

265
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,540
反正你穿着也比她好看
Looks better on you anyway.

266
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:25,030
山姆
Sam.

267
00:23:25,130 --> 00:23:26,930
那是你父亲的剑
That's your father's sword.

268
00:23:27,410 --> 00:23:29,110
是我家族的剑
It's my family's sword.

269
00:23:33,970 --> 00:23:35,320
山姆
Sam.

270
00:23:35,380 --> 00:23:37,010
他不会想要夺回去吗
Won't he come for it?

271
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:41,250
他大可一试
He can bloody well try.

272
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:48,270
狮子和玫瑰喜结良缘
The lion and the rose are one.

273
00:23:48,270 --> 00:23:50,550
感谢天上诸神
I thank the gods above.

274
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:52,940
对你  我美丽的新娘
And to you, my beauteous bride,

275
00:23:52,940 --> 00:23:55,480
我许诺永恒的爱
I pledge undying love.

276
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:59,830
乔佛里国王万岁  玛格丽王后万岁
Hail King Joffrey. Hail Queen Margaery.

277
00:23:59,870 --> 00:24:02,250
我要敬我的新王后一杯
I'll drink a toast to my new queen,

278
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:04,400
没有比她更美的女人
for there is no one fairer.

279
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:06,880
亲爱的舅舅  你愿意分享我的喜悦
Dear Uncle, will you share my joy

280
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:09,210
为我斟酒吗
and be my royal cupbearer?

281
00:24:09,210 --> 00:24:11,830
多喝一点甜酒
Drink long and deep, my noble king,

282
00:24:11,830 --> 00:24:13,920
我高贵的国王
from this cup of sweet wine.

283
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:16,860
这会是他喝的最后一杯酒
The last drink he shall ever take.

284
00:24:16,870 --> 00:24:19,360
这是我的复仇
And vengeance shall be mine.

285
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:32,240
有毒
Poison!

286
00:24:32,980 --> 00:24:34,280
谋杀
Murder!

287
00:24:34,280 --> 00:24:37,380
我气喘吁吁  我死期将近
I gasp. I-- I die.

288
00:24:39,250 --> 00:24:40,440
我踉踉跄跄
I limp.

289
00:24:42,460 --> 00:24:44,640
是他
And it was he...

290
00:24:45,770 --> 00:24:47,550
毒死了我
that poisoned me.

291
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:50,360
我恶毒的舅舅小恶魔
My evil Uncle Imp.

292
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:04,340
我的长子
My firstborn son.

293
00:25:05,080 --> 00:25:06,900
我的黄金狮子
My golden lion

294
00:25:07,370 --> 00:25:09,820
被卑鄙错误地杀死
foully, falsely slain.

295
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:13,980
愿你能够安息
I pray you found a lasting peace

296
00:25:14,370 --> 00:25:16,680
免受冲突和痛苦
free from strife and pain.

297
00:25:18,810 --> 00:25:20,940
听听我的祈祷  残忍的诸神
Hear my prayer, Oh cruel gods.

298
00:25:20,950 --> 00:25:22,800
让我替他去死
Take my life instead.

299
00:25:23,190 --> 00:25:26,610
我亲爱的儿子死了  我也活不下去
For I cannot face another day when my sweet boy is dead.

300
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:28,470
悲伤
Oh, woe.

301
00:25:30,060 --> 00:25:31,740
痛苦
Oh, grief.

302
00:25:33,410 --> 00:25:36,880
最黑暗的日子  我的心充满哀痛
Oh, darkest day, my heart is full of sorrow.

303
00:25:39,710 --> 00:25:41,370
希望通通破灭
All hope is lost.

304
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:44,990
快乐烟消云散
All joy is gone.

305
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:50,220
明天也不复存在
And there is no tomorrow.

306
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,660
我听到闻到的是什么
What is that I hear and smell?

307
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:16,540
马上就会被我送入地狱的人
Someone I'll soon send to hell.

308
00:26:16,540 --> 00:26:19,470
是时候见证传言的真假了
It's time to see if truth they told

309
00:26:19,470 --> 00:26:23,040
据说泰温·兰尼斯特能拉出黄金
who said Tywin Lannister shits gold.

310
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:27,130
你这个禽兽  禽兽
You beast. You beast.

311
00:26:27,130 --> 00:26:31,940
你害死了我的妻子  现在又杀了自己的父亲
You killed my wife and now you've taken your father's life.

312
00:26:31,980 --> 00:26:35,080
没有比你更大逆不道的儿子了
No worse child ever stained this land.

313
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:37,220
我诅咒为你命名的那一天
Curse the day I named you.

314
00:26:46,830 --> 00:26:50,770
这是我最大的罪孽  现在我得跑了
My greatest crime. Now I must flee.

315
00:26:50,770 --> 00:26:53,360
我要穿过狭海
Then sail across the Narrow Sea

316
00:26:53,360 --> 00:26:57,340
背叛你到底
to do unto you more treachery.

317
00:26:57,630 --> 00:27:01,820
不要畏惧寒冬  畏惧我吧
Don't fear winter. Fear me!

318
00:27:05,670 --> 00:27:07,000
谢谢
Thank you.

319
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:11,000
女士们先生们  让我们感谢比安卡
Ladies and gentlemen, I give you Bianca,

320
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:12,880
克莱恩佐
Clarenzo.

321
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,580
感谢博邦奴
I give you Bobono.

322
00:27:16,760 --> 00:27:19,120
和卡迈罗
I give you Camello.

323
00:27:20,200 --> 00:27:21,740
最后  我们最出色的
And last but not least,

324
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:23,910
亲爱的克连恩夫人
sweet Lady Crane.

325
00:27:35,530 --> 00:27:38,920
好好拍打  把跳蚤打出来  这可是宝贝
Give this a good beating. Shake those fleas out. That's a dear.

326
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:41,140
那些观众都是白痴
That crowd was shit.

327
00:27:45,620 --> 00:27:46,780
丫头
Girl.

328
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:49,260
你在后台做什么
What are you doing back here?

329
00:27:50,620 --> 00:27:51,770
没做什么
Nothing.

330
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:54,900
那天我在观众里见过你
I saw you the other day in the audience.

331
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:57,570
这出愚蠢的戏你看过几次了
How many times have you seen this stupid play?

332
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:01,160
三次
Three times.

333
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:02,430
你付过钱吗
Did you pay?

334
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,820
没有
No.

335
00:28:08,660 --> 00:28:10,990
我记得那时候戏班子来我的村子演出
I remember when the players came to my village.

336
00:28:10,990 --> 00:28:13,140
我身上一分钱都没有  就偷偷溜进去了
I didn't have any money, so I snuck in.

337
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,750
跟你现在一样
Just like you.

338
00:28:15,740 --> 00:28:17,950
看着上了妆的脸蛋  戏服
Saw the painted faces, the costumes,

339
00:28:17,950 --> 00:28:19,670
听着他们唱歌
listened to the songs,

340
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:23,140
在年轻的恋人死在对方怀里时放声大哭
cried when the young lovers died in each other's arms.

341
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,780
第二天我就逃离村子加入了他们
I ran off and joined them the next day,

342
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:26,980
再也没回头
never looked back.

343
00:28:28,430 --> 00:28:29,880
你演得真好
You're very good.

344
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:32,250
我最后的几句台词糟透了
My final speech is shit.

345
00:28:32,260 --> 00:28:34,970
但是公平地说  我总喜欢这么告诉自己
But to be fair to myself, which I always like to be,

346
00:28:34,970 --> 00:28:36,560
是剧本写得不怎么样
the writing's no good.

347
00:28:37,560 --> 00:28:38,980
那就改写
So change it.

348
00:28:40,970 --> 00:28:42,320
这出戏如果没有你
It would all just be farting, belching,

349
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:43,940
就只剩下放屁打嗝扇耳光了
and slapping without you.

350
00:28:45,410 --> 00:28:47,130
你会怎样改写剧本
How would you change it?

351
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:55,820
王后爱他的儿子  胜过世上的一切
The queen loves her son more than anything.

352
00:28:56,800 --> 00:28:59,380
但她连道别的机会都没有  他就死掉了
And he was taken from her before she could say good-bye.

353
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:01,340
