She wouldn't just cry.

354
00:29:05,170 --> 00:29:06,830
她应该愤怒
She would be angry.

355
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:10,610
她渴望杀死那个令她伤心的人
She would want to kill the person who did this to her.

356
00:29:14,770 --> 00:29:16,260
你叫什么名字
What's your name?

357
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:19,250
茉慈
Mercy.

358
00:29:20,390 --> 00:29:23,060
你的眼睛会说话  茉慈
You have very expressive eyes, Mercy.

359
00:29:23,850 --> 00:29:25,610
眉毛也漂亮
Wonderful eyebrows.

360
00:29:26,230 --> 00:29:28,350
你喜欢扮演角色吗
Do you like pretending to be other people?

361
00:29:30,140 --> 00:29:32,900
我得走了  我父亲在等着我呢
I have to go. My father's waiting for me.

362
00:29:41,100 --> 00:29:43,560
克连恩夫人  观众们爱死你了
Lady Crane, they loved you.

363
00:29:44,050 --> 00:29:46,720
他们太热情了  或者醉得厉害
They were sweet. Or drunk.

364
00:29:47,420 --> 00:29:49,010
热情到醉
Drunkenly sweet.

365
