奈德死的那一幕没人笑
No laugh for Ned's death.

366
00:29:51,250 --> 00:29:54,360
这群观众猪狗不如
These people are worse than animals.

367
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:58,500
但是他们爱她  他们都爱她
But they loved her. They all love her.

368
00:29:58,940 --> 00:30:02,160
没错  崇拜你的是猪狗不如的观众
Yes, you are adored by people and animals alike.

369
00:30:02,160 --> 00:30:04,220
我尽量在这种基础上发挥
I do what I can with what I'm given.

370
00:30:05,190 --> 00:30:06,620
哪种基础
With what you're given?

371
00:30:07,040 --> 00:30:08,760
我只是在思考...
Well, I was thinking--

372
00:30:08,760 --> 00:30:10,700
我们现在都是思考者了吗
Oh, we're all thinkers now, are we?

373
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:13,170
大奶子里全是想法
Full to the tits with ideas.

374
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:16,750
-我不是说...  -你有想法  我有想法
