00:30:18,610 --> 00:30:21,520
我的想法为什么比你们的更有价值
Why should my ideas have any more value than yours

377
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:24,030
就是因为我这辈子都在干这一行吗
simply because I've been doing this my whole life?

378
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:27,110
谁有资格来评判我的作品
Who is anyone to judge my work?

379
00:30:27,110 --> 00:30:29,410
这是我的专业  我知道自己在做什么
This is my profession. I know what I'm doing.

380
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:32,390
你没有权利发表意见
You have no right to an opinion.

381
00:30:45,400 --> 00:30:47,030
小心那个人
Careful of that one.

382
00:30:51,730 --> 00:30:53,390
她想要你死
She wants you dead.

383
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:34,220
怎么样
And?

384
00:31:34,430 --> 00:31:36,170
跟我预想的一样
As I expected.

385
00:31:38,290 --> 00:31:39,620
真遗憾
A shame.

386
00:31:40,060 --> 00:31:42,150
女孩天份不错
A girl had many gifts.

387
00:31:45,490 --> 00:31:47,030
你答应过我
You promised me.

388
00:31:53,180 --> 00:31:54,830
别让她受罪
Don't let her suffer.

389
00:32:46,860 --> 00:32:49,750
全体停止前进
Company, halt!

390
00:32:51,250 --> 00:32:52,460
队长大人
My lord.

391
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,140
提利尔大人
My lord.

392
00:32:55,670 --> 00:32:59,900
朋友们  这个时刻到了
My friends, the hour has come.

393
00:33:00,410 --> 00:33:03,760
疯狂已经控制了这座城市
Madness has overtaken this city

394
00:33:03,760 --> 00:33:08,320
我的孩子们身陷魔爪
and grasped in its claws my children.

395
00:33:08,800 --> 00:33:11,790
但是现在  我们必须将其
But now we must drive it back

396
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:14,830
打回石头缝里的老家
under the rocks whence it came.

397
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:19,410
疯狂的末日已至
Madness has had its day!

398
00:33:22,740 --> 00:33:25,230
全体前进
Forward, march!

399
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:30,810
不管富人还是穷人  贵族还是平民
Rich or poor, noble or common,

400
00:33:31,920 --> 00:33:35,500
如果我们有罪  就必须赎罪
if we sin, we must atone.

401
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:39,800
提利尔家族的玛格丽
Margaery of House Tyrell

402
00:33:39,980 --> 00:33:42,300
以罪人的身份面对我们
came to us a sinner.

403
00:33:42,950 --> 00:33:44,570
她站在大教堂里
She stood before the gods

404
00:33:44,570 --> 00:33:47,140
在诸神面前撒谎
in the holy sept and lied.

405
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:50,250
她对自己哥哥的罪行视而不见
She turned a blind eye to her brother's sins.

406
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:52,540
她羞辱了自己的家族
She disgraced her house,

407
00:33:53,170 --> 00:33:56,630
羞辱了她的国王  和她自己
her king, and herself.

408
00:34:28,350 --> 00:34:30,270
全体停止前进
Company, halt!

409
00:34:30,270 --> 00:34:32,090
向前看
Face front!

410
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:33,800
转身
Turn!

411
00:34:36,020 --> 00:34:37,390
提利尔大人
Lord Tyrell.

412
00:34:39,450 --> 00:34:40,650
詹姆爵士
Ser Jaime.

413
00:34:41,750 --> 00:34:43,240
抱歉打扰了
Sorry to interrupt.

414
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:46,170
我们为玛格丽王后和洛拉斯·提利尔爵士而来
We're here for Queen Margaery and Ser Loras Tyrell.

415
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:48,840
把他们交出来我们就离开
Give them to us and we'll be on our way.

416
00:34:50,160 --> 00:34:53,050
我无权把他们交给你
I don't have the authority to give them to you.

417
00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:56,320
你也无权带走他们
And you don't have the authority to take them.

418
00:34:56,370 --> 00:34:58,080
说得对
That's right.

419
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,080
驾
Hyah.

420
00:35:07,290 --> 00:35:08,920
上矛
Lock spears!

421
00:35:10,920 --> 00:35:14,580
我代表拜拉席恩家族的国王托曼一世
I speak for King Tommen of House Baratheon, First of His Name.

422
00:35:14,690 --> 00:35:18,020
诸神在此事上不认可他的权威
The gods don't recognize his authority in this matter.

423
00:35:18,060 --> 00:35:20,670
你已经侮辱了一个大家族
You've already insulted one great house.

424
00:35:20,890 --> 00:35:22,690
不会再有第二次
It won't happen twice.

425
00:35:22,690 --> 00:35:24,800
在玛格丽·提利尔上街之前
Every last sparrow will die

426
00:35:24,800 --> 00:35:27,620
我们会杀死所有的麻雀
before Margaery Tyrell walks down that street.

427
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:29,910
为侍奉诸神而死
To die in the service of the gods

428
00:35:29,920 --> 00:35:32,240
我们死得其所
would please each and every one of us.

429
00:35:32,420 --> 00:35:34,080
我们求之不得
We yearn for it.

430
00:35:43,910 --> 00:35:46,050
但今天不是时候
But there is no call for it today.

431
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:52,100
不会有赎罪之旅
There will be no walk of atonement.

432
00:36:09,110 --> 00:36:10,530
收阵
Order up.

433
00:36:10,530 --> 00:36:13,850
玛格丽王后已经通过将另一人
Queen Margaery has already atoned for her sins

434
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:16,290
引入七神的圣光之下
by bringing another

435
00:36:16,460 --> 00:36:19,120
赎清了她的罪孽
into the true light of the Seven.

436
00:36:48,810 --> 00:36:51,440
我们在此共同宣布
Together we announce

437
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:54,590
和谐的新时代开启
a new age of harmony.

438
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:57,140
王权与信仰
A holy alliance

439
00:36:57,550 --> 00:37:00,910
神圣的联合
between the Crown and the Faith.

440
00:37:17,570 --> 00:37:20,490
托曼国王万岁  诸神保佑您  玛格丽王后
Long live King Tommen and bless you, Queen Margaery!

441
00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:23,010
王权与信仰
The Crown and the Faith

442
00:37:23,350 --> 00:37:26,660
是这个世界赖以依存的两大支柱
are the twin pillars upon which the world rests.

443
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:32,020
我们将携手重筑七国的荣耀
Together we will restore the Seven Kingdoms to glory.

444
00:37:50,870 --> 00:37:52,470
怎么回事
What's happening?

445
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,510
他打败了我们
He's beaten us.

446
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:56,320
就是这么回事
That's what's happening.

447
00:38:11,710 --> 00:38:14,980
攻击信仰  就是攻击王权
When you attack the Faith, you attack the Crown.

448
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:17,690
任何攻击王权的人都不应当
Anyone who attacks the Crown is unfit

449
00:38:17,700 --> 00:38:20,180
担任御林铁卫队长
to serve as Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.

450
00:38:20,550 --> 00:38:24,160
在你出生以前我就是御林铁卫的一员了
I've been a member of the Kingsguard since before you were born.

451
00:38:26,140 --> 00:38:29,140
你不必这样做  你什么都不需要做
You don't have to do this. You don't have to do anything.

452
00:38:31,860 --> 00:38:33,690
我必须听从诸神的指示
I have to answer to the gods.

453
00:38:33,700 --> 00:38:36,080
在你还坐在王座上的时候就不需要
Not when you're sitting in that chair.

454
00:38:40,120 --> 00:38:42,780
身为国王  我意已决
The Crown's decision on this matter is final.

455
00:38:44,730 --> 00:38:47,210
我要裸体游街吗
Will I be walking naked in the streets?

456
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:50,340
还是先在圣堂地牢里待几个月
Or will I spend a few months in the Sept dungeons first

457
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:52,590
学学诸神是如何仁慈
to teach me about the gods' mercy?

458
00:38:56,860 --> 00:38:58,530
你为你的家族
You have served your house

459
00:38:58,530 --> 00:39:00,660
和国王效忠了多年
and your king faithfully for many years.

460
00:39:01,310 --> 00:39:02,920
你也将继续如此
And you will continue to do so.

461
00:39:05,210 --> 00:39:06,840
但不是在这个城市
But not in this city.

462
00:39:10,170 --> 00:39:13,430
你搞丢了
You've lost it?

463
00:39:15,650 --> 00:39:16,600
是的  父亲
Yes, Father.

464
00:39:16,600 --> 00:39:19,560
那是城堡  又不是羊
It's a castle, not a bloody sheep.

465
00:39:19,950 --> 00:39:22,390
你应该还知道它在哪儿
Presumably you still know where it is.

466
00:39:22,980 --> 00:39:25,060
你没有搞丢奔流城
You didn't lose Riverrun.

467
00:39:25,130 --> 00:39:27,350
你是让黑鱼夺走了它
You let the Blackfish take it from you.

468
00:39:27,350 --> 00:39:30,280
他突袭了我们  他比任何人都更了解奔流城
He surprised us. He knows the castle better than anyone.

469
00:39:30,290 --> 00:39:33,780
红色婚礼之后你倒是搞丢了黑鱼
You did lose the Blackfish after the Red Wedding.

470
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:36,880
他就在这个厅里  你却让他离开了
You had him right here in this hall and you let him leave.

471
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:39,060
然后当我要你去追捕并杀了他时
Then when I told you to hunt him down and kill him,

472
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:40,340
你找不到他了
you couldn't find him.

473
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:43,130
这才叫搞丢了
That's what it means to lose something.

474
00:39:43,130 --> 00:39:45,840
现在他回来夺走了奔流城
Now he's come back and taken Riverrun.

475
00:39:47,260 --> 00:39:48,840
我觉得不该怪我们...
I don't think it's fair to blame us--

476
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:52,050
我们匍匐在徒利家脚下长达三百年
For 300 years we kissed Tully boots,

477
00:39:52,060 --> 00:39:55,990
向他们及其腥臭的鳟鱼旗宣誓效忠
swore oaths to them and their stinking fish banners.

478
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:58,420
再也不会了  奔流城是我们的
Not again. Riverrun is ours.

479
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,920
夺回来
Take it back.

480
00:40:00,850 --> 00:40:02,160
我们没有人手
We don't have the men.

481
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:05,800
我们的人手十倍于该死的黑鱼
We've got 10 times as many men as the damn Blackfish.

482
00:40:05,970 --> 00:40:09,230
梅利斯特家已与我们为敌  还有布莱伍德家
The Mallisters have risen against us. And the Blackwoods.

483
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:12,280
无旗兄弟会正在召集平民对付我们
The Brotherhood Without banners is rallying the commoners against us,

484
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:14,340
抢劫我们的供给车队和军营
raiding our supply trains and camps.

485
00:40:14,340 --> 00:40:17,320
奔流城能在围城战中抵抗一年
Riverrun can withstand a siege for a year.

486
00:40:18,210 --> 00:40:21,060
我如果找借口  就会让她管事
If I want excuses, I'll put her in charge.

487
00:40:21,060 --> 00:40:22,800
他们在嘲笑我们
They're laughing at us.

488
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,870
从河间地
All across the Riverlands

489
00:40:24,870 --> 00:40:26,570
到君临城
right down to King's Landing,

490
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:28,560
他们在嘲笑我们
they're laughing at us.

491
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,870
我睡觉也能听见
I hear it in my sleep!

492
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:34,640
不幸的是  我还没死
I'm not dead yet, unfortunately for you.

493
00:40:34,640 --> 00:40:36,170
并且在他们笑得哽住之前
And I'll not leave this world

494
00:40:36,170 --> 00:40:38,980
我不会离开这个世界
until they all choke on that laughter.

495
00:40:39,210 --> 00:40:41,190
夺回城堡
Take that castle back.

496
00:40:42,890 --> 00:40:45,120
他不会屈服的  父亲
He'll never yield, Father.

497
00:40:45,520 --> 00:40:47,930
他会的
Oh, he'll yield.

498
00:40:52,600 --> 00:40:54,680
你  给他看你捅进婊子的肚子
You'll show him the knife

499
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:59,030
杀了罗柏·史塔克孩子的那把刀
you used to kill Robb Stark's child in his whore mother's belly,

500
00:40:59,300 --> 00:41:01,030
而你  给他看你割开
and you'll show him the knife

501
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:03,660
他侄女喉咙的那把刀
you used to open his niece's throat.

502
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:05,240
你们要提醒他
And you'll remind him

503
00:41:05,240 --> 00:41:09,370
一开始在红色婚礼上结婚的是谁
who it was that got married at the Red Wedding in the first place.

504
00:41:10,150 --> 00:41:11,300
他的侄子
His nephew.

505
00:41:27,130 --> 00:41:29,070
高兴点  艾德慕大人
Cheer up, Lord Edmure.

506
00:41:29,930 --> 00:41:31,350
你要回家了
You're going home.

507
00:41:32,220 --> 00:41:35,100
我被派去对付黑鱼
I'm being sent to deal with the Blackfish.

508
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:38,100
显然瓦德·佛雷自己处理不了
Apparently Walder Frey can't manage it on his own

509
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:40,200
因为他已经四百岁了
because he's 400 years old.

510
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:42,610
让我带兵前往奔流城
Sent me with an army to the Riverlands

511
00:41:42,610 --> 00:41:44,590
打一场能持续数月的围城战
and a siege that could last months.

512
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:47,260
无论你带兵去哪儿
Better you're elsewhere at the head of an army

513
00:41:47,260 --> 00:41:49,020
都好过被关在圣堂的地牢
than in the sept dungeons.

514
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:51,870
我不去河间地
I'm not going to the Riverlands.

515
00:41:55,100 --> 00:41:56,030
那怎么办
What, then?

516
00:41:56,670 --> 00:42:00,250
我要给波隆金子  数不胜数的金子
I'm going to give Bronn the largest bag of gold anyone's ever seen

517
00:42:00,640 --> 00:42:03,070
让他去召集最好的杀手
and have him gather the best killers he knows.

518
00:42:03,660 --> 00:42:04,890
我带他们去大圣堂
I'll take them to the sept

519
00:42:04,890 --> 00:42:06,720
我要摘下大麻雀的脑袋
and I'll remove the High Sparrow's head

520
00:42:06,720 --> 00:42:08,890
还有我能找到的每一只麻雀的脑袋
and every other sparrow head I can find.

521
00:42:08,900 --> 00:42:09,640
不行
You can't.

522
00:42:09,650 --> 00:42:12,010
我们儿子在他手里  他抢了我们的儿子
He has our son! He stole our son!

523
00:42:12,860 --> 00:42:14,440
他拆散了我们家
He's torn our family apart.

524
00:42:14,440 --> 00:42:17,150
我们应该怎么对待拆散我们的人
How should we treat people who tear us apart?

525
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:20,520
我们应该毫不留情  我们也绝不会仁慈
We should treat them without mercy and we will.

526
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:23,970
可如果杀了大麻雀  你没法活着走出圣堂
But if you kill the High Sparrow, you won't leave the sept alive.

527
00:42:23,970 --> 00:42:25,860
没了你  这一切都毫无意义
And without you, this is all for nothing.

528
00:42:27,540 --> 00:42:30,060
统领我们的军队  那才是属于你的位置
Stand at the head of our army where you belong,

529
00:42:30,740 --> 00:42:32,110
也是父亲对你的希望
where Father wanted you.

530
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:35,570
让我们的军队知道他们该效忠谁
Show our men where their loyalties belong.

531
00:42:35,570 --> 00:42:37,580
让他们看看兰尼斯特的本事
Show them what Lannisters are,

532
00:42:37,580 --> 00:42:39,680
我们对待敌人的手段
what we do to our enemies.

533
00:42:41,080 --> 00:42:43,260
夺回那座愚蠢的小城堡
And take that stupid little castle back

534
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:45,700
因为它本就属于我们  因为你有这个能力
because it's ours and because you can.

535
00:42:45,710 --> 00:42:48,900
你即将面临审判  我要留下来陪你
You'll stand trial soon. I need to be here for you.

536
00:42:50,030 --> 00:42:52,040
那是比武审判
It will be a trial by combat.

537
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:54,950
我有魔山
I have the Mountain.

538
00:42:57,680 --> 00:43:00,360
他们让我们更强大  我们所有人
They've made us both stronger, all of them.

539
00:43:01,980 --> 00:43:03,990
他们不知道我们有多强
They have no idea how strong we are.

540
00:43:04,540 --> 00:43:06,580
不知道我们准备如何对付他们
No idea what we're going to do to them.

541
00:43:17,180 --> 00:43:18,850
我们一直在一起
We've always been together.

542
00:43:19,600 --> 00:43:21,480
以后也会一直在一起
We'll always be together.

543
00:43:22,140 --> 00:43:24,270
这世上只剩我们两个了
We're the only two people in the world.

544
00:43:44,750 --> 00:43:46,150
为什么救我们
Why did you help us?

545
00:43:49,650 --> 00:43:51,220
三眼乌鸦派我来的
The Three-Eyed Raven sent for me.

546
00:43:51,220 --> 00:43:52,640
三眼乌鸦死了
The Three-Eyed Raven's dead.

547
00:43:53,500 --> 00:43:54,720
现在他又活了
Now he lives again.

548
00:44:07,580 --> 00:44:09,930
上次见你  你还是个小孩
When I last saw you, you were a boy.

549
00:44:11,410 --> 00:44:12,560
无所畏惧
A fearless boy.

550
00:44:13,200 --> 00:44:16,880
喜欢爬城墙  让他母亲担心坏了
Loved to climb the castle walls, frighten his mother.

551
00:44:17,740 --> 00:44:18,650
你是谁
Who are you?

552
00:44:36,950 --> 00:44:38,190
班扬叔叔
Uncle Benjen.

553
00:44:39,930 --> 00:44:41,100
琼恩写来的最后一封信上说
The last letter Jon wrote me

554
00:44:41,110 --> 00:44:42,840
你在长城外失踪了
said you had been lost beyond the Wall.

555
00:44:46,290 --> 00:44:48,670
我带着游骑兵深入北边
I led a ranging party deep into the North

556
00:44:48,670 --> 00:44:50,170
去寻找异鬼
to find white walkers.

557
00:44:51,600 --> 00:44:52,650
他们找到了我们
They found us.

